About Us
Oceans Golf Club is a privately owned not-for-profit golf course that is open to the public (all ages) for 13-hole, Par 3 golf fun in Daytona Beach Shores, Florida.
​Oceans Golf Club would like to welcome you to play on our beautifully maintained course. We strive to offer excellent customer service and an enjoyable experience playing Golf.
​
Call us with questions at:
386.788.2998
